Stilta helps in-house teams move fast on exactly this kind of filing: rapid prior art searches across all asserted patents, claim-chart analysis to identify the strongest invalidity positions, and PTAB/IPR filing strategy to create leverage before litigation costs compound.

If it would be useful, we can put together a focused overview of how we would approach the four patents here. Happy to set up a short call at your convenience.

